INSERT INTO `music_sargams` (`id`,`song_names`,`sargam`,`url`) VALUES (377,'Apki ankhon me kuchh - Notes & Sargam','Singer : Lata ÔÇô Kishore Kumar\n Lyricist : Gulzar,\n Music : Rahul Dev Burman,\n Movie : Ghar (1978)\nI have tried to produce Sargam notes for this evergreen romantic song on my G# scale flute taking Re as the first note.┬á This song is based on Raag ÔÇÿKedarÔÇÖ which was the favourite raag of R D Burman.┬á He had composed maximum number of his songs in this raag, including his last song ÔÇ£Kuchh na kahoÔÇªÔÇØ.\nThere are lots of places in this song where you need to use ÔÇÿMeendÔÇÖ ( ~ ) to get the wavy effect, and ÔÇÿMurkiÔÇÖ ( { } ) for the ÔÇÿharkatsÔÇÖ in the song.\nHope this Sargam notation makes you happy when you play it on your instruments.┬á IÔÇÖm sure once you get a hang of this song, you will not get tired of playing it over and over again.┬á Good Luck!\n','Notes---Sargam-Apki-ankhon-me-kuchh');
