INSERT INTO `music_sargams` (`id`,`song_names`,`sargam`,`url`) VALUES (417,'Tujhe dekh dekh sona - Notes & Sargam','Film : Kaliyug (2005)\n Singer : Rahat FA Khan\nTujhe dekh dekh sona\n SR G R G R GPGRS\n Tujhe dekh dekh sona\n S R G R G R GPGRS\n Tujhe dekh kar hain jagna\n SR G R G G R GPGRS\nMaine yeh zindagani\n R R R R S D R\n Sang tere bitaani\n R R R R S D R\n Tujhmein basi hain meri\n R R R S R G R\n jaaan haaai\n G R S G R S\n \njiya dhadak dhadak\n P P S D D S D D\n jiya dhadak dhadak\n P P S D D S D D\n jiya dhadak dhadak\n P P S D D R S\n Jaaayen\n D PP\n jiya dhadak dhadak\n P P S D D S D D\n jiya dhadak dhadak\n P P S D D S D D\n jiya dhadak dhadak\n P P S D D SR S\n Jaaayen\n D PP\nFlute\n PP SDD SDD PP SDD SDD PP SDD SR S DPP\nKabse hai dil mein mere\n S RG R D D D D\n armaan kai ankahe\n PGP P DS P G P\n \nInko tu sunle aaja\n P P P R GP G R\n chaahat ke rang chadha jaa\n P P P R G P G R\n \nKehna kabhi to mera\n R R R S R G R\n maaan haaai\n G R S G R S ||\n \nJiya Dhadak\n \n','Notes---Sargam-Tujhe-dekh-dekh-sona');
INSERT INTO `music_sargams` (`id`,`song_names`,`sargam`,`url`) VALUES (418,'Tu Mile Dil Khile - Notes & Sargam','Sargam notaions for the romatic song ÔÇÿTu mile dil khileÔÇªÔÇÖ\nSinger \n: Alka Yagnik ÔÇô Kumar Sanu\nLyrics\n: Indeevar, \nMusic \n: M.M.Kreem, \nMovie \n: Criminal (1995)\nWhen at first I tried to jot down the notaions for this song,┬á using Suddh Re and Dha, I was constantly missing out on the finer tunes of the song.┬á Then I tried to search for the Raag on which this song was based and found out that┬áthis song is based on Raag Bhairavi, that essentially uses all the Komal Swaras, viz.,┬á\nre, ga, dha and ni\n.┬á After learning this, I replaced Shudh Re and Dha with their Komal counterparts, and all the blocks of puzzle fell in place!┬á┬á\nI used C# flute to produce the Sargam for this song.┬á Signs and symbols used are : Small letters = Komal Swars, ()=Kann Swar, ~=Meend.┬á┬áThis is a difficult song for the beginners to play on flute as it includes use of half holes for producing the komal notes.┬á But, with little practice, specially of Raag Bhairavi, one can surely pull it.┬á┬á\n','Notes---Sargam-Tu-Mile-Dil-Khile');
