INSERT INTO `music_sargams` (`id`,`song_names`,`sargam`,`url`) VALUES (468,'O majhi re - Notes & Sargam','Sargam ( notation ) for song O majhi re\n Singer : Kishore Kumar\n Film : Khushboo (1975)\nA sheer masterpiece by the Trio Magicians ÔÇô RD+KK+Gulzar, this song is my all time favourite.┬á What a composition, what lyrics and what singing!! Simply out of this world.┬á You just have to listen to this song with eyes closed, and you will in no time be floating on a boat.\nJotting down the notations proved to be a tough task for me, even tougher than the flute cover that I made for this song (click the link at the end).┬á I played it on my F# flute, taking first note as ÔÇ£ReÔÇØ.┬á There are many places in this song which makes it so lovable, like, the dipping tune on the word ÔÇ£KinaraaaaaÔÇØ, the interlude music with flutes, the ÔÇ£puk-pukÔÇØ sound with the bottle, etc.┬á I have tried my best to note down the Sargam notations of all these ÔÇô may not be to the perfection, but workable.\nHope you will enjoy these notations on your instruments.\nPRELUDE\n (Bottle, Guitar, Rythm)\nR RRR | P | P (x4)\nMUKHDA:\nO | Maajhi | Re,\n R | MM | PÔÇª\nApanaa | Kinaaraa,\n PM~M~R | R ,N ,NÔÇª..n\nNadiyaa | Ki┬á | Dhaaraa | Hai\n ,N ,N R | R | MÔÇª M | PÔÇª\nO | Maajhi | Re\n R | M D| D(n)D PÔÇª\nINTERLUDE \n(Violins)\nP DNÔÇª | DN DN SÔÇÖÔÇª | RÔÇÖGÔÇÖRÔÇÖSÔÇÖ RÔÇÖÔÇª\nANTARA:\nSaahilon | Pe | Bahane | Vaale\n PÔÇª N DN | DP | PP N | DN DP\nKabhi | Sunaa To | Hogaa | Kahin, | O\n PP | N DN DP | PGÔÇª P | PP | N DD PDP\nHo, | Kaagazon | Ki | Kashtiyon Kaa\n PÔÇª | PÔÇª N DN | DP | P N | DN DP\nKahin | Kinaaraa | Hotaa | Nahin\n PP | N DN DP | PGÔÇª P | PP\nHo Maajhi | Re | Maanjhi | Re\n N NNÔÇª | SÔÇÖÔÇª.~D |┬á DMM | PÔÇª\nMUSIC (Violins):\n \nRG MGRS ,N R P\nKoi | Kinaaraa | Jo | Kinaare | Se | Mile | Vo,\n N N | N D~N N | D~P | P D~N N | D~P | PP~DÔÇª(N)D | P MG\nApanaa Kinaaraa Hai\n S G | G MÔÇª M | PÔÇª\nMUSIC (Flute):\n \n(S)RÔÇÖÔÇª~N | N SGRSN | DNSNDPMG | RMGR SRÔÇª\nO┬