INSERT INTO `music_sargams` (`id`,`song_names`,`sargam`,`url`) VALUES (522,'Kahin door jab din dhal jaye - Notes & Sargam','Sargam notations for the song : Kahin door jab din dhal jaye\n Singer : Mukesh\n Lyrics : Yogesh\n Music : Salil Chowdhury\n Movie : Anand (1971)\nThis song is very close to my heart. Magical composition by Sali Chowdhury, amzing lyrics by Yogesh and soulful singing of Mukesh.┬á ┬á Just the song that I wish to listen again and again when I am sad.\nI had been trying to write the notations for this song from quite some time now.┬á But I would get stuck after the prelude tune which I would start with Ga for easiness.┬á But after the prelude I would not get the correct note of the first word ÔÇ£kahinÔÇØ in the song.┬á I kept on trying and trying.┬á And then, today I tried something different.┬á I started the prelude tune with High Sa on G# flute.┬á That was it.┬á After starting the prelude of the song on high sa, I was able to come to the correct note for ÔÇ£kahinÔÇØ which was Dha.\nI really enjoy playing this song on my flute.┬á I have tried to jot down the prelude, interlude and music pieces in between the song as below.┬á Hope you will also enjoy this evergreen song on your instruments.\n','Notes---Sargam-Kahin-door-jab-din-dhal-jaye');
